    "stat_block": {
        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "The shaft of this bolt is scorched and blackened, and handling it coats your fingers with a fine black powder. When an activated *disintegration bolt* hits a target, it's subject to a *disintegrate* spell requiring a DC 34 Fortitude save. As with the spell, a critical hit on the attack roll causes the target's saving throw outcome to be one degree worse.",
